b">乗</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">の</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>せてお<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">城</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">しろ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">連</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">つ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>れて行きました。そしてあまんじゃくの<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">首</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">くび</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">斬</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">き</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>り<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">落</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">お</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>として、<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">畑</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">はたけ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">隅</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">すみ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">捨</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">す</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>てました。その<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">首</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">くび</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>から<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">流</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">なが</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>れ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">出</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">だ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>した<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">血</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ち</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>が、きび<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">殻</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">がら</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>にそまって、きびの<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">色</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">いろ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>がその<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">時</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">とき</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>から<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">赤</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あか</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>くなり<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">出</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">だ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>しました。<lb />
